Three specials have been broadcast on [[BBC One]] between 25 December 2005 and 30 December 2007. The specials vary in length. ''[[One Flew Over the Cuckoo Clock]]'' was fifty minutes long, ''[[From Here to Paternity]]'' was forty-five minutes long while ''[[The Special Relationship]]'' was forty minutes long. A 2009 [[List of The Green Green Grass episodes|Christmas Special]] is expected to broadcast late 2009.
